				<div class="talk-intro">
					<p id="tagline" class="notranslate">Hans Rosling reframes 10 years of UN data with his spectacular visuals, lighting up an astonishing -- mostly unreported -- piece of front-page-worthy good news: We're winning the war against child mortality. Along the way, he debunks one flawed approach to stats that blots out such vital stories.</p>
											<p>
							In Hans Rosling’s hands, data sings. Global trends in health and economics come to vivid life. And the big picture of global development—with some surprisingly good news—snaps into sharp focus. <a target="_blank" title="Hans Rosling's bio" href="/speakers/hans_rosling.html">Full bio »</a>						</p>
					
											<div id="attributionText">
													</div>
									</div>

